  "Title": "OpenClaw has an arbitrary transcript path file write via gateway sessionFile",
  "Description": "In OpenClaw versions prior to 2026.2.12, the gateway accepted an untrusted `sessionFile` path when resolving the session transcript file. This could allow an authenticated gateway client to create and append OpenClaw session transcript records at an arbitrary path on the gateway host.",
